Right?

00:42:49.980 --> 00:42:50.240
SERGEI SARAKHANOV: Yeah.

00:42:50.240 --> 00:42:50.390
Yeah.

00:42:50.390 --> 00:42:51.330
Here in Dublin.

00:42:51.330 --> 00:42:53.621
SPEAKER: How do you like it,
working with Irish people?

00:42:53.621 --> 00:42:55.590
How do you feel,
